        "title": "feat: Hermes 遷移 — automation、telegram、strategy-engine 與核心模組整合",
        "body": "## Summary\n- 擴充 automation 引擎：排程系統、工作流編輯器、任務面板、contracts.tools\n- 更新 Telegram 頻道：textMode 支援、互動回覆 payload、群組聊天可見回覆\n- 新增 evolution-learning AI Agent Mesh ABCD 認知層\n- 新增 strategy-engine、dmad-engine 及 tradingagents-bridge 腳本\n- 更新核心模組：plugins circuit-breaker、agents、gateway trading、cron\n- 更新 Control UI：trading desk 視圖、i18n 繁中翻譯、agent 面板\n- 修復 pre-commit hook Windows ENAMETOOLONG（分批處理）\n- 新增 pre-push build 驗證 hook\n- 清理 .gitignore 加入臨時生成檔案\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n**Behavior addressed**: Build 編譯、Gateway 連線、MCP 伺服器、doctor 健康檢查皆在真實 OpenClaw 環境驗證通過\n\n**Real environment tested**: Windows 11, Node.js v24.14.1, pnpm workspace, OpenClaw 2026.5.5 (4280fa7), Gateway port 18789, Claude Code MCP\n\n**Exact steps or command run after fix**:\n1. 執行 pnpm build 驗證所有模組編譯成功\n2. 執行 openclaw doctor --fix 修復 UI assets、plugin registry、config\n3. 執行 openclaw health 確認 Gateway 運行\n4. 透過 Claude Code MCP 連線確認 openclaw MCP server 正常\n5. git push 觸發 pre-push hook 驗證 build\n\n**Evidence**:\n```\n$ pnpm build\nOK: All 4 required plugin-sdk exports verified.\n[copy-hook-metadata] Copied 5 hook metadata files.\n\n$ openclaw doctor --fix\nUI build complete.\nPlugin registry refreshed: 70/122 enabled plugins indexed.\n\n$ openclaw health\nTelegram: configured\nGateway event loop: ok max=67ms p99=44ms util=0.037 cpu=0.021\nAgents: dev (default), main\nSession store (dev): 29 entries\n\n$ git push (pre-push hook output)\n[pre-push] ✅ Build 驗證通過\n```\n\n**Observed result after fix**: 所有模組正確編譯、Gateway 正常運行 (event loop ok, util=0.037)、MCP 連線成功、pre-push hook 驗證通過、doctor 無殘留錯誤\n\n**What was not tested**: live trading 功能未在生產環境測試；Telegram bot 互動未做 E2E 測試（需真實 bot token）；extensions/evolution-learning 未做端對端整合測試\n\n## Test plan\n- [ ] CI 全通過（CodeQL 固有模式除外）\n- [x] pnpm build 成功\n- [x] Gateway health check 通過\n- [x] MCP openclaw 連線正常\n- [x] pre-push hook 驗證通過\n\n🤖 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)",
